  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research is to search for reproducible changes in a wide range of&#xD;
      physical signals, including heart rate, muscle tone and activity and EEG before and at the&#xD;
      onset of seizures in patients with epilepsy.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
